textAfterTable: Interests Golf Travel Beaches Church My business About Me "Why have you never been married?" I was engaged during college, and Lord knows there have been several along the way that would have been great but I really never thought that I would still be single. PS. I also have five sisters. I have a blessed life, spiritually, financially - awesome family and friends. I thank God for that daily. It's time to find a great woman, successful, comfortable and confident who likes to get dressed up but it just as comfortable, casual, in a pair of jeans who loves laughter and humor. Often travel to resorts in Mexico - Cabo, Cancun, Mazatlan to play golf and hang out at the beach and pool and meet fantastic people from all over the world. Enjoy all sports - especially Ranger baseball - awesome to just hang out at the ballpark and enjoy the smells and atmosphere. Politically active - conservative.
